. Your award of RSUs hereunder shall be settled in whole Shares. Fractional Shares shall not be issuable hereunder and any fractional Share shall be disregarded. Except as specifically provided otherwise in this Section 8, Shares subject to an award of RSUs hereunder shall only be issued and distributed to you in a single sum of whole
8. Settlement of Award and Distribution of Shares
Shares within the 75-day period after the end of the Restriction Period. Notwithstanding the foregoing, in the event that your RSUs become vested due to death, Disability or a Change in Control, the award of RSUs hereunder shall be settled in a single sum of whole Shares within the 75-day period after such vesting. In the event that any such 75-day period begins in one calendar year and ends in another, you (or your beneficiary as the case may be) shall not have the right to designate the calendar year of payment. Moreover, notwithstanding the foregoing, if you are a Specified Employee, a distribution of Shares may not be made until within the 30-day period commencing with the first day of the seventh month following the month of any Separation from Service for reasons other than Disability or a Change in Control, or, if earlier, your death, except as maybe otherwise permitted under Section 409A.
